        { "Title", "\240\159\143\134 RANKED" },
        { "Description", "There have been a lot of changes made to Ranked. Let\'s get straight into it!" },
        { "Description", "Players that are ranked Platinum 1 or higher now no longer receive Daily ELO Shields. This feature was intended to encourage newer players to play Ranked and serves no purpose in the higher ranks" },
        { "Description", "Default weapons are now bannable if everyone in the duel owns more than 4 weapons in each slot. We want to promote loadout diversity in Ranked and we only expect top players (whom should be comfortable playing all weapons) to be affected by this change" },
        { "Description", "It\'s evident that so far during Season 0, ELO gain/loss calculations have not been the best. On top of that, there were matchmaking issues that impacted the integrity of the Ranked scene" },
