        { "Description", "We\'ve also introduced ELO Decay \226\128\148 Players ranked Onyx 1 or higher are now required to play atleast 1 Ranked game every 7 days to avoid ELO Decay. Inactive players will lose 100 ELO per day until they start playing Ranked again or until they hit the bottom of Onyx" },
        { "Description", "Due to all of these changes and due to the how unfair ELO progression & matchmaking was during the first phase of Season 0, all players with an ELO of 3,400+ have been reset back down to 3,400. ELO Resets are not something we expect to do again, especially after this experimental Season 0 concludes" },
